sentences.sentence: This is fen country – the mills drive pumps that drain the land.
sentences.translation: 这是一个沼泽国 - 这些工厂启动水泵排干地面积水。

sentences.sentence: The national heroine of the day was Xing Fen, winner of the first gold medal of the Games.
